Class HttpResponse

Incontrast to HttpRequest objects which are created automatically by Django 
HttpResponse objects are your responsibility

Usage

Passing strings

Typical usage is to pass contents of the page, as a string
to the HttpResponse constructor

   from django.http import HttpResponse
   response = HttpResponse()
   
 Passing iterators
 
 Setting header fields
 
 Telling the browser to treat the response as a file attachment
 
